Davido. Photo: BellaNaija While OBO Davido has been dropping series of hit songs from his DMW record label like the viral Naija love song Assurance, he seems to be cooking something big with this next song “NWA BABY” Although the title “NWA BABY” seems to be suggesting another love song about his girlfriend Chef Chioma, he has admitted that the song might be the biggest feature of his entire career as he urged fans to pray for him in his tweet below. Keep me in your prayers I might have just recorded the Biggest feature of my career that can literally change my life and also I Finally got a release date for ‘NWA BABY’ … clear your playlist !! Daddy coming !! — Davido (@iam_Davido) July 26, 2018 